name: Robbers Roost Canyon (North Fork)
description:
Introduction

The first drop is an easy downclimb. The second drop is a spicy downclimb and handline may be helpful; there is a chockstone hidden underneath the big chockstone one can lower 5 feet onto and from there and easy downclimb the final 6 feet. There are two required rappels. The exit up the Crack Canyon is a bonus and really elevates the technical fun.
